page.title: 09TRACY'S DAY AT HOME
page.content: Woke up at 07.33. Had a sore throat.Put my jeans and T-shirt on. Downstairs I had breakfast;poached egg on toast. Went over to the shops to get some cough sweets. Played rounders,then went in and watched T.V. Had my dinner of cheese sandwiches, crisps and cake. Went upstairs to play my violin. Had a cup of tea and a jam-tart. Watched T.V. Had tea of pork steaklets and mashed potatoes. washed up. Got Stephen(brother) ready for cubs. Dropped him off at 6.30, then went to my Aunty's in Coventry. (Coventry is about 8 miles away from where I live.) Returned home in the car picking up Stephen on the way. Went to bed, watched T.V. until 10.15, then fell asleep. My name is Tracy Hancock. I am 12 years old. The date is the 6th May 1985.
